    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1000 Waves is a game about progression as the player's ultimate goal is to clear all 1000 waves and defeating the final boss. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated dungeons hinder the movement of the player as they must maneuver around and avoid hazardous obstacles that may appear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/ccede5cef62a69fe1bd8b715ca507706.avif?t=1732230873\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras_big/ccede5cef62a69fe1bd8b715ca507706.avif?t=1732230873 width=800 height=512 /></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Within the center of the arena powerups will spawn the will temporarily enhance the player. A vast amount of unique enemy types will be encountered as you make your way to the 1000th wave. Utilize an array of unique weapons where some are more beneficial than others towards defeating certain enemy types.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/322326dc2f4a7ae1600bbaf4d311420a.avif?t=1732230873\" width=296 height=272 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 25th wave you will encounter a tail pickup necessary for utilizing the bomb function and can be useful towards blocking enemy bullets and swiping away enemy swarms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/53ba1a07366112c7d97a9c73e35f01cb.avif?t=1732230873\" width=280 height=228 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally 0-3 perks have a chance at spawning that will boost many aspects of one's playthrough such as stronger bombs and enhancing powerup abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/68b5a218e6a66412e0e33c94ef65bec2.avif?t=1732230873\" width=372 height=596 /></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience points are gathered via destroying enemies, collecting multiplier gems, and completing objectives within a certain amount of time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/f0f90c95b6939328c36f6870416fddbd.avif?t=1732230873\" width=132 height=96 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A few objectives include but are not limited to:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pathway - Following a defined number of points, reaching 0 completes the objective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/9f271631d2b5818adc4c3aa0295b1044.avif?t=1732230873\" width=218 height=216 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defend - Destroy surrounding enemies before they collide with the objective, when the timer runs out it completes the objective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/3abc07d19af12f39a0ee22ab0e85a56d.avif?t=1732230873\" width=266 height=268 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maneuver - Collect a defined number of orbs scattered around the arena before time runs out, once they have all been brought to the main objective it will be completed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/9fa05a14b2e231c6a933a9a8baaf3c65.avif?t=1732230873\" width=348 height=404 /></span></p></li></ul></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience points gained can  be used to level up your ship in many ways such as increased firepower, heightened defense capabilities, and powerup longevity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312510/extras/ca61f3fa72119ce05f9f10261c296ea1.avif?t=1732230873\" width=800 height=160 /></span></p></li></ul>",
